Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really disliked in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:07.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,though I didn't have any close friends either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:12.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never really part of a clique.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:14.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I join?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice you, Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:18.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:22.43,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, a classmate named Shino-chan said...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:28.78,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't mean to say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:29.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:30.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:31.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And I became the “Sadako girl.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:38.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people in my middle school thought it was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako really does seem like she has a psychic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:42.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised if she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:44.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, I was the “psychic aura girl.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when I came to high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Sadako has a psychic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:56.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you lock eyes with her for 3 seconds, a week later...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:01.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,One rumor led to another, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:10.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, maybe I was fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:15.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a bit depressed at times, but I don't think I was ever really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, remember that rumor about Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Yano and Yoshida backing her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:25.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:30.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san aren't backing me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:41.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal and the slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:51.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:00.07,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls' washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fight in the washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:06.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako and the girls from Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were inside earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Sadako started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about the rumors about Chizu and Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:26.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff about Chizu-san being covered in blood and doing a hundred guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Sadako's spreading the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to try my best to be their friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma wouldn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma's trying to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about those rumors about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:54.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you holding something in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:02.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:06.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.99,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:37.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:44.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nice? They're going to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:57.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said all that stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about Yoshida being a delinquent and Yano being a slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:04.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:10.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one spreading rumors about Yoshida and Yano, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she got shoved down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:28.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I say that about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:33.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, they're really kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:37.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something we want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:47.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were probably just hanging out with you for the hell of it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:51.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably sick of you by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:06:00.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just started hanging out with them to get close to Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:03.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now they're in the way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost. Be by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll get off your—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to get off my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the hell—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:40.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snack time. Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:55.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't avoid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, my jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:06.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how kind they were to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:21.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I more than just like them... I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:28.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:32.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still sticking up for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after all those rumors she spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our problem, so piss off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:24.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? This isn't your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking to Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in my middle school, so you must know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:37.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About my 99 consecutive victories dueling against guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:44.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mess with Sadako again and I'll mess you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:49.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that stuff... it really is a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:58.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:09.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, Yoshida-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the rumor was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:54.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for believing in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we do something to piss you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:05.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:14.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hate stupid rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:21.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew those rumors about Yano and Yoshida were bullshit, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously thought Kuronuma would do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:30.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:34.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe she did, since it was a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:37.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako was defending them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defending them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after she got pushed down,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was defending Yano-san and Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:47.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:51.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yano-san and Yoshida-san came to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:55.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Yano and Yoshida helped Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:02.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it really was bullshit then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:05.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Sadako's notes were good, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I aced the exam yesterday thanks to those notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:18.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I totally thought it was just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma's going to be so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when she finds out that it was thanks to Hirano and Endou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:27.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Hirano, Endou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Make the most of it, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:37.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could stop the rumors by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:39.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:45.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I could do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“It didn't work out.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Oh well.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:53.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept wanting to fit in with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:56.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but somewhere inside I'd already given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:03.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I couldn't give up on you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it meant that there'd be bad rumors about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you might get hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:17.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't give you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:26.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to make you feel better when you get hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:31.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:35.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:41.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to be closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:44.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there are more rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:59.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're listening to me, without even looking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:11.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be friends with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:17.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you thought we were hurt because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:27.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we would get hurt by you being around us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:34.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still wanted to be with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you were hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:44.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, I'm dirty right now, I just fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:59.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said everything I was about to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:05.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed for having doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:08.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get used to being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:17.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know? We adore you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:23.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming friends happens before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:29.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were already friends, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.43,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We were?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:43.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I'm going to hug you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to start a rumor again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you cry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're teary-eyed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:15:05.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell one of those horror stories now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:14.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's crying and laughing at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:23.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem pretty happy together though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:24.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:33.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They switched roles, and now it's solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I won't have to cheer her up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:45.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:56.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:00.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this rotten teen drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:16.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, all of you!\NLike the bugs that you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:38.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I always heard what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:44.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“Go for it, go for it...”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't she...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:54.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...smiling just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that, I totally saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:13.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Exams ended, and my grades were horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Sadako 30th?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's still pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first day was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:25.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the class average was up dramatically for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:28.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay for Sadako's notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zashiki warashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:34.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako warashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's just me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:44.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think everyone looks at me just a little differently these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:50.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I made a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat ramen, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:18:00.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, we haven't heard your horror story yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have money, Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:15.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a chance to be alone with her anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.24,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had ramen in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go hang out, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:26.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I was just reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:31.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:36.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I have people to care for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.19,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you know? Friends eat ramen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:42.76,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.10,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't be fooled, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:47.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something that I couldn't do on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:19:01.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to take her from them when she looks so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong Kazehaya, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:19.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you became friends, just like you wanted. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:28.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:31.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just acknowledged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say about us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:45.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You more than like us, you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:20:01.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You love us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:09.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things have changed since I met Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned a lot of new feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, tell that horror story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:23.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There once was a Biwa player named Houichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Miminashi Houichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:30.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-san was seriously pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:33.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he hates stupid rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about us, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sort of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:48.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka's really liked Kazehaya since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:12.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he's going to hate you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:28.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My precious time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:33.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Saturday Night
